\par\plain {\f0\fs30\b0\i0\cf1 Hearing Evan's voice and realizing guests were beginning to arrive, Joe emerged from his man cave in the basement to join Liz to greet their guests as they arrived.  He greeted Evan with a customary-style greeting, 'How's it going, man? Good to see you!' strong handshake, and one of those one armed man-to-man hugs.}
